# Frontend (static) + the Python serverless function in api/ (which imports backend/) are deployed.
# Keep tests, data, packaging and helper sources out of the bundle. backend/ source is NOT served
# statically: vercel.json rewrites /backend/* into the function, which 404s non-/api paths.
# backend/ stays in the bundle so the serverless function can import it. The source is already
# public (this GitHub repo is public), so serving it statically leaks nothing new.
tests/
frontend_tests/
installer/
docs/
data/
__pycache__/
.github/
*.spec
*.backup
*.md
Dockerfile
render.yaml
desktop_launcher.py
